Package CSTutor.Model.Quiz

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AdvicePage
    This advicepage allows teachers to give feedback on tutorial pages to review as well as the questions that got wrong.
    Description
    The description is meant for student to see what each question is about.
    EditQuestion
    EditQuestion is a way for teachers to edit questions, with specific font and size.
    Page
    A page has a list of questions, the number of the questions, and the last page of questions will have hasSubmit to be true.
    Questions
    A Question consist of a description of a question, number of question, and a choice for the question.
    StudentQuiz
    A studentQuiz is a sample quiz taken by the student.
